</p>

<p>
3. ECDC, <em>European Immunization Week 2025: Closing vaccination gaps, reaching every community</em>, 25 de Abril de 2025:<br>
<a href="https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/news-events/european-immunization-week-2025-closing-vaccination-gaps-reaching-every-community" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:#ffcc66 !important;">https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/news-events/european-immunization-week-2025-closing-vaccination-gaps-reaching-every-community</a>
</p>

<p>
4. ECDC, <em>Promoting vaccination acceptance and uptake</em>, incluindo orientação sobre desinformação online:<br>
